    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p><em>Greeting: \"The frigid veil persists.\" | Response: \"All the world in winter's white.\" | Parting: \"May her blessing chill you.\"</em></p><p>One coldwind governs each Ten-Towns settlement, overseeing all cult activity and interfacing with town Speakers as recognized clergy. Their eyes are solid blue ice orbs \u2014 the Blessing of the Frostmaiden. They scribe their own holy books (The Reliance of Sleet and Glacier). Spellcasting: Wisdom, save DC 15, +7 attack. 7th-level caster.</p><p><strong>Renown 25 | CR 4</strong></p><p><em>Signature spells: frostbite, ice talon, frost fingers, absorb cold, heat thief.</em></p>"
